Kind: captions
Language: ar

00:00:16.700 --> 00:00:19.700
Arabic Spring " Revolutions"

00:00:20.700 --> 00:00:29.700
After defeating colonization, Arab peoples started to feel hopeful about a prosperous future.

00:00:30.700 --> 00:00:45.700
that their efforts to kick out colonization, is not in vain. Unfortunately, ruling regimes didn't meet peoples' hope for Freedom and Justice,

00:00:46.700 --> 00:00:56.700
not even coping with scientific and industrial development. Their life was the furthest from prosperity. 

00:00:57.700 --> 00:01:08.700
During decades, many layers of political and financial corruption have piled.

00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:15.700
Life conditions in these countries, have deteriorated in all fields .

00:01:16.700 --> 00:01:30.700
Corruption reached citizens' daily life, people felt their livelihood and their health is threatened.

00:01:30.700 --> 00:01:40.700
Some jobs became restricted to some specific classes. Unemployment spread due to governments' failure in applying projects.

00:01:40.700 --> 00:01:55.700
Arab citizens suffered a lot hoping for a better future. Though, abstention continued a lot, middle classes disappeared, expensiveness spread and corruption kept increasing.  

00:01:55.700 --> 00:02:11.700
Ruling regimes didn't know that they had implanted revolution seeds and that pressing with congestion has to lead to an explosion. 

00:02:11.700 --> 00:02:30.700
Peoples upraised against dictators to start a new phase of looking for justice and freedom.

00:02:31.700 --> 00:02:45.700
It became valued more than any time that human rights have to stand before any other demands.

